# Claudex — RedLantern Studios cross-engine OS repo
# Track the OPERATING SYSTEM layer only: instructions, state, frameworks, governance, memory.
# NOT product code. NOT secrets. NOT large binaries.

# Exclude everything by default
*

# --- Re-include the OS layer ---
!.gitignore
!README.md
!CLAUDE.md
!AGENTS.md
!CTP_FRAMEWORK.md
!BUILD_CONSTITUTION.md

!.claude/
!.claude/**
!swarmclaw/
!swarmclaw/**
!OPS/
!OPS/**
!memory/
!memory/**
!context/
!context/**
!docs/
!docs/**

# --- Hard exclude SECRETS (override re-includes above; last match wins) ---
OPS/API_KEY_VAULT.md
OPS/SKILL_API_KEY_VAULT.md
OPS/ENV_VARS.md
**/*API_KEY_VAULT*
**/*KEYS_REFERENCE*
**/*keys_reference*
.env
.env.*

# --- Hard exclude large / binary / generated ---
*.pdf
*.docx
*.xlsx
*.pptx
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.mp4
*.zip
*.tar
*.gz
*.log
node_modules/

# --- Re-include brand logos last (override *.png; last match wins) ---
!rls_logo.png
!rls_logo_v2.png
